From Nancy Patricia O'Connor Subject Re Amusing atheists and agnostics Bake Timmons writes Rule Don't mix apples with oranges How can you say that the extermination by the Mongols was worse than Stalin Khan conquered people unsympathetic to his cause That was atrocious But Stalin killed millions of his own people who loved and worshipped him and his atheist state How can anyone be worse than that You're right And David Koresh claimed to be a Christian